star-triangle equations, Inversion relations, Integrable models, Iterated
mappings, Automorphisms of algebraic curves, \nobreak{Dynamical} systems,
Elliptic curves, Cremona transformations, Fermat numbers, cyclotomic
polynomial.\par }\vskip 1cm
